p.e:
YES!                                          YES!
                   YES              YES!

I'VE FIGURED IT OUT! I HAVE THE
INSIGHT!
I FOUND THIS RITUAL CAVE WHERE
THE VEIL BETWEEN WORLDS IS SO
THIN I CAN SEE IT!

STOLE THIS SPELLBOOK FROM
MISS ELANORE. I'VE BEWITCHED IT
WITH A TRANSLATION SPELL SO
ANYONE CAN READ THE RUNES.
EVEN YOU.
YES YOU,  [OWN PERSON].

PLACE YOUR HAND ON THE PAGE
I'VE LEFT THE BOOK OPEN TO.
        FOLLOW ME.
                                  CROSS OVER.
